fr.maxlego08.itemstacker.command.VCommand
Direct Known Subclasses:
CommandItem, CommandItemReload, CommandItemVersion
public abstract class VCommand extends Arguments
Abstract class representing a command in the plugin. Handles sub-commands, permissions, arguments, and tab completions.
